STARTER ITEMS/DINOS PACK:
- Medical Brew, Energy Brew x10;
- Cooked Meat and Tranq Arrows x50;
- Metal Pickaxe, Hatchet, Sickle, Pike, Crossbow x1;
- Hide Armor Set x1;
- Flashlight, Filled Water Jar, Sleeping Bag, Atomic Spyglass x1;
- Cryopods x5;
- Max Imprinted LVL 250 Pteranodon + Saddle x1;
Aaaand a Special gift from me: a fresh Beer and a lucky featherd Max Imprinted LVL 250 friend (Hint: He have the same Lystro buff power!);

In order to claim your free Starter here you have to buy it for free from the GoldCoin Shop ingame by opening up your Inventory for console players (hold R for PC Players).
Then move your Left Stick / Mouse and click over the House icon near your GoldCoin amount Icon.

Now you should see every items yuo can buy for Gold Coins, but to see the Starter Pack item you need to click on the 2nd Icon with the Loot Crate image.
You can ONLY CLAIM 1 so... be carefull, find a safe spot before open the bag!
To leave the Shop Menu click outside the Shop UI with A/X/Mouse.

The GoldCoin Shop and the Exchange Shop can always be updated anytime, so always check them to see if something changed, Player Shops too!

Hold R (PC), X (XBOX) or SQUARE (PS5) to open the Radial Mods Menu to find the mods you can configure to use as you wish.
